title: Ann Bond - A Guide to the Harpsichord.pdf
description:
A Guide to the Harpsichord

Author - Ann Bond

Format - PDF

Requested


This practical guide examines the mechanics and evolution of the instrument and offers a survey of its literature. The author discusses touch and technique, including articulation and fingering, and the issues involved in historical performance practices. She also provides suggestions on selecting and maintaining a harpsichord.
